imx-bootlets: Fix cmdlines for Linux boot

This adapt the cmdlines for the partitioning layout used on the
generated SD cards.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [configuration]

Signed-off-by: Otavio Salvador <otavio@ossystems.com.br>

